desc.en: ITB is the center of economic development under the future of mouse science and technology. It is a project developed by young people. It has the value of future regional ecology. ITB coin creates value at the beginning.
desc.zh: ITB是小老鼠科技创立未来下经济开发为中心，是一项由年轻人开发出项目，有未来区域生态的价值的货币，ITB币的初心创造价值！
